{"tid":1943254,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[官方成績表]CCTVB下半年廣告暴跌35%","createTime":"2020-03-25T14:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T04:19:19.000Z","uid":345840,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b571833dc3f178efeeafb2e8b0b354c329a46a64","tid":1943254,"uid":345840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nnn75JQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnn75JQ.jpg&h=b7511273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔離POST有人睇業績，唔明點解報紙話TVB下半年少左5億廣告<br />\n其實只將全年業績減左上半年業績<br />\n再計返下半年俾人抵制果半年條數出黎<br />\n咁就睇得出<br />\n<br />\nTVB戰線手足話CCTVB廣告少左四成，而戰線7月先成立<br />\n下半年個分部收入少左成35%，足證跌四成係絕無誇大<br />\n<br />\n好啦，你加入左戰線未呢?一齊送CCTVB上路啦<br />\n<br />\n抵制tvb戰線 - 杯葛廣告商<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Sbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=3ee33a91\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\n全城抵制東方廣告商<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/boycottoncc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fboycottoncc&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Sbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=7a3b9327\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/boycottoncc</a>"},{"pid":"3c31bad2f6bc5f54509f2fedea07fcab26460a86","tid":1943254,"uid":202707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:33:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dee16ba467586945125a00f8924373e323fa8fa5","tid":1943254,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6c6827fce2d5c8c5d002cc0208d321407523dc","tid":1943254,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77045ccbd9868a5